data.description: Beautiful beach home just a short stroll to the white sandy beaches and emerald waters of the Florida gulf coast. Located in the heart of Panama City Beach this  home features an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Recently remodeled inside and out. Kitchen has granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Large deck and pergola with plenty of room for entertaining. Fenced back yard with swimming pool. Walk to Pier Park and enjoy all the shopping, restaurants and entertainment. A very short drive to 30A, several state parks and the airport. All of this in a great neighborhood with no HOA fees. This home would make an ideal investment, primary or secondary home.
